title: Game Character High Elf Sound Effects
description: Summon a legendary High Elf character in your next game! Welcome in “Game Character High Elf” to the ESM's sound library family. He’s arrogant, thinks of himself as a high born and vanquishes the enemy at every turn.
longDescription:
Audio Demos

Video Demos

This High Elf character voice over collection is filled with over 400+ well thought out, scripted dialogue lines, battle cries, fight vocals, vocalizations and everything you need to create stunning cut scenes, compelling immersive in-game experiences & more.

Game Character High Elf features fantasy male voice over samples inspired by hit fantasy games like Guild Wars, and World of Warcraft.. The High Elf voice texture is a deep tone, with a smooth performance and works well as a strong unbreakable protagonist game character. With this pack you get to be the first line of defense against the enemy in your next score, trailer, game, or project. Darken the skies with elven arrows and charge!

Delivered in 44.1k 16Bit .wav file format, Game Character High Elf not only gives you clean and recognizable sound your audience will enjoy but provides you with all the vocal elements you need to build the story! Mix and match the sound files, to construct your story how you want it. Your allies are under attack.. What are you going to do? Game Character High Elf, Available Now!
